Version 0.6.1 - 2003.02.26
* based on 0.5.1 source code
* add color on display
* show version in title
* use parameter to set mydict root dir
* set locale toggle button during startup
* update configure.in to autocheck whether -lintl is needed. not perfect solution.

Version 0.5.4,0.5.5,0.5.6,0.6.0 - 2003.02
* update to stdc++ class
* remove recite features 

