* improve gds format (correct phonetic display)

Version 0.5.0 - 2002.10.10
* add support bdc (gds format, see http://www.pgy.com.cn )

Version 0.4.2 - 2002.10.6
* add check for english platform
* fix bug on solaris platform , NULL point  

